time_high":266.3,"all_time_low":85.5,"long_business_summary":"Precision Electronics Limited designs and manufactures communication and electronics products and solutions in India. The company offers telescopic, light duty, medium duty, heavy duty, and specialised masts; light duty, medium duty, elevator, and heavy duty tripods; positioners; and multi-function active junction box. It also provides major accessories, such as base plate, tilting cup, nails, hammer, guy rope, foot pump, pegs, erection stand, earthing kit, lightning arrestor, drive on frame, hand held pendant, cable, pneumatic controller unit, guy rope controller, sand kit, de spanner, adjustable spanner, plier, box spanner with T, teflon tape, scew driver, steel oil can, velcro cable strap for cable tie, levelor, allen keys, guy marker, nail puller, roto mould, plastic injection moulding, canvas, air compressors, vehicle mounting brackets, payload adapter, side mounting payload, circular heavy duty bracket, dual payload, dual mount, interface adapter, and tripods adapter. In addition, it offers technology solutions, including SIGINT and jamming, telecom, radio networking, and BEV chargers; turnkey SITIC, warranty, AMC, environmental, and ESS test lab services, as well as manufactures cable harness, metal forming, box builds, and complex assembly products. The company serves telecom, hi-tech, security, government, and automotive sectors. Precision Electronics Limited was incorporated in 1979 and is headquartered in Noida, India."}}